gomodel:SYNGO_469  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Debated whether expressed in brain but data in Figure 1C supports expression of transcript. VMAT antibody (SC15313 of limited characterization) hints at cellular expression in hippocampus. Immunofluorescence co-localization with this VMAT antibody and synaptophysin suggesting synaptic vesicle location.. Experimental description: VMAT/KO mice (B6.129P2-Slc18altm1Dgen/J created at Deltagen" ;
